General.Name: Acroud AB
General.Description: Acroud AB (publ) owns, develops, and operates comparison and news sites in Sweden. The company operates through iGaming Affiliation and Software as a Service (SaaS) segments. It also engages in the Casino, Poker, and Betting business. In addition, the company develops and offers SaaS solutions in the affiliate industry; and provides streaming services, as well as runs the gaming event " The Festival Series. Further, it offers media creator access to a large pool of gaming campaigns. The company was formerly known as Net Gaming Europe AB (publ) and changed its name to Acroud AB (publ) in July 2020. Acroud AB (publ) was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in St. Julian's, Malta.
